<span class="t s4" style="left:238px;bottom:1087px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.01px;">Finally, our moderation tools and teams can collect additional data as part of their </span>
<span class="t s4" style="left:238px;bottom:1072px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.01px;">investigations. Where legally allowed, we can also receive information about suspected or </span>
