<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:996px;letter-spacing:-0.15px;word-spacing:0.03px;">The Homee service is intended for users aged 18 years and over. We do not knowingly collect </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:978px;letter-spacing:-0.14px;word-spacing:0.02px;">personal information from individuals under 18. If we become aware that we have collected such </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:959px;letter-spacing:-0.14px;word-spacing:0.03px;">information, we will take reasonable steps to delete it. </span>
<span class="t s4" style="left:119px;bottom:930px;letter-spacing:0.12px;">Data generated </span>
