<span class="t s4" style="left:119px;bottom:887px;letter-spacing:0.13px;">Usage Data </span><span class="t s4" style="left:238px;bottom:887px;letter-spacing:0.11px;">Using the service generates data about your activity, including how you use it (e.g. when </span>
<span class="t s4" style="left:238px;bottom:873px;letter-spacing:0.09px;word-spacing:0.03px;">you created an account, paid features you’ve used) We may also receive data related to </span>
<span class="t s4" style="left:238px;bottom:858px;letter-spacing:0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">interactions you had with our ads on third party’s websites or apps. </span>
<span class="t s4" style="left:119px;bottom:843px;letter-spacing:-0.06px;word-spacing:0.17px;">Technical Data </span><span class="t s4" style="left:238px;bottom:843px;letter-spacing:0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">Using the service involves the collection of data from and about the device(s) you use to </span>
<span class="t s4" style="left:238px;bottom:829px;letter-spacing:0.09px;word-spacing:0.02px;">access our service, including hardware and software information such as IP address, </span>
<span class="t s4" style="left:238px;bottom:815px;letter-spacing:0.11px;">device ID and type, apps settings and characteristics, app crashes, advertising IDs and </span>
<span class="t s4" data-mappings='[[6,"fi"]]' style="left:238px;bottom:801px;letter-spacing:0.11px;">identiﬁers associated with cookies or other technologies that may uniquely identify a </span>
<span class="t s4" style="left:238px;bottom:786px;letter-spacing:0.04px;word-spacing:0.07px;">device or browser. For more information about cookies, see our Cookie Policy. </span>
