<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:493px;letter-spacing:-0.15px;word-spacing:0.02px;">personalizing your experience, and helping you get the most out of Homee. We also process your </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:475px;letter-spacing:-0.15px;word-spacing:0.02px;">data to keep you—and all members of the Homee community—safe and secure while using the </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:456px;letter-spacing:-0.14px;word-spacing:0.02px;">app. This is a responsibility we take very seriously, and we’re constantly improving our systems </span>
